        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1337/10673/1337_10673_000007_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1337",
        "content": "\"My cousin,\" he exclaimed, \"I do not know how to thank you for your kindness.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1337_10673_000007_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1337/10673/1337_10673_000007_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1337",
        "content": "Farewell.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1337_10673_000008_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1337/10673/1337_10673_000008_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1337",
        "content": "\"I don't understand.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1337_10673_000009_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1337/10673/1337_10673_000009_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1337",
        "content": "\"No matter,\" he replied, \"go back by the path that you came.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1337_10673_000014_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1337/10673/1337_10673_000014_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1337",
        "content": "My persecutor, however, did not stop here.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1337_10673_000014_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1337/10673/1337_10673_000014_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1337",
        "content": "He shut me up in a large case and ordered his executioner to carry me into a desert place, to cut off my head, and then to abandon my body to the birds of prey.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1337_10673_000018_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1337/10673/1337_10673_000018_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1337",
        "content": "\"My dear nephew,\" he said, \"your story gives me some hope.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1337_10673_000020_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1337/10673/1337_10673_000020_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1337",
        "content": "However, we passed through the smoke into a large chamber, which at first seemed quite empty.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1337_10673_000021_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1337/10673/1337_10673_000021_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1337",
        "content": "This horrible sight turned me faint, but, to my surprise, my uncle did not show so much surprise as anger.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1337_10673_000027_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1337/10673/1337_10673_000027_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1337",
        "content": "It was sunset, and I paused for a little to look about me, and to decide which way to turn my steps.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1337_10673_000030_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1337/10673/1337_10673_000030_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1337",
        "content": "\"I am satisfied,\" replied Zobeida; \"you can go when you like.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1337_10674_000005_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1337/10674/1337_10674_000005_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1337",
        "content": "\"Madam,\" said the young man, addressing Zobeida, \"if you wish to know how I lost my right eye, I shall have to tell you the story of my whole life.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1337_10674_000006_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1337/10674/1337_10674_000006_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1337",
        "content": "I was taught first to read and write, and then to learn the Koran, which is the basis of our holy religion, and the better to understand it, I read with my tutors the ablest commentators on its teaching, and committed to memory all the traditions respecting the Prophet, which have been gathered from the mouth of those who were his friends.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1337_10674_000006_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1337/10674/1337_10674_000006_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1337",
        "content": "I also learnt history, and was instructed in poetry, versification, geography, chronology, and in all the outdoor exercises in which every prince should excel.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1337_10674_000007_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1337/10674/1337_10674_000007_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1337",
        "content": "However, as was my duty, I took with me ten camels, laden with rich presents for the Sultan.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1337_10674_000008_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1337/10674/1337_10674_000008_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1337",
        "content": "I managed to jump off without any injury, and looked about to see if I was pursued.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1337_10674_000009_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1337/10674/1337_10674_000009_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1337",
        "content": "Luckily my wound was only a slight one, and after binding it up as well as I could, I walked on for the rest of the day, till I reached a cave at the foot of a mountain, where I passed the night in peace, making my supper off some fruits I had gathered on the way.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1337_10674_000011_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1337/10674/1337_10674_000011_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1337",
        "content": "The tailor listened with attention, but his reply, instead of giving me consolation, only increased my trouble.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1337_10674_000012_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1337/10674/1337_10674_000012_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1337",
        "content": "\"Beware,\" he said, \"of telling any one what you have told me, for the prince who governs the kingdom is your father's greatest enemy, and he will be rejoiced to find you in his power.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1337_10674_000016_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1337/10674/1337_10674_000016_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1337",
        "content": "This counsel was very distasteful to me, but I thought I could not do otherwise than adopt it.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1337_10674_000016_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1337/10674/1337_10674_000016_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1337",
        "content": "So the next morning I set out with a company of poor wood cutters, to whom the tailor had introduced me.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1337_10674_000017_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1337/10674/1337_10674_000017_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1337",
        "content": "I was hacking at the root of a tree, when I beheld an iron ring fastened to a trapdoor of the same metal.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1337_10674_000017_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1337/10674/1337_10674_000017_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1337",
        "content": "I soon cleared away the earth, and pulling up the door, found a staircase, which I hastily made up my mind to go down, carrying my hatchet with me by way of protection.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1337_10674_000017_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1337/10674/1337_10674_000017_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1337",
        "content": "When I reached the bottom I discovered that I was in a huge palace, as brilliantly lighted as any palace above ground that I had ever seen, with a long gallery supported by pillars of jasper, ornamented with capitals of gold.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1337_10674_000017_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1337/10674/1337_10674_000017_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1337",
        "content": "Down this gallery a lady came to meet me, of such beauty that I forgot everything else, and thought only of her.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1337_10674_000018_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1337/10674/1337_10674_000018_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1337",
        "content": "To save her all the trouble possible, I hastened towards her, and bowed low.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1337_10674_000020_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1337/10674/1337_10674_000020_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1337",
        "content": "\"A man, madam,\" I replied; \"I have nothing to do with genii.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1337_10674_000023_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1337/10674/1337_10674_000023_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1337",
        "content": "For a long while I did nothing but weep, and would not suffer the genius to come near me; but time teaches us submission, and I have now got accustomed to his presence, and if clothes and jewels could content me, I have them in plenty.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1337_10674_000026_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1337/10674/1337_10674_000026_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1337",
        "content": "\"What you ask is impossible,\" she answered; \"but stay here with me instead, and we can be happy, and all you will have to do is to betake yourself to the forest every tenth day, when I am expecting my master the genius.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1337_10674_000027_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1337/10674/1337_10674_000027_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1337",
        "content": "Awful though you think him, he shall feel the weight of my arm, and I herewith take a solemn vow to stamp out the whole race.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1337_10674_000028_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1337/10674/1337_10674_000028_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1337",
        "content": "\"If you do, it will be the ruin of both of us,\" said she; \"I know genii much better than you.\" But the wine I had drunk had confused my brain; I gave one kick to the talisman, and it fell into a thousand pieces.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1337_10674_000029_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1337/10674/1337_10674_000029_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1337",
        "content": "\"Princess!\" I cried, \"what is happening?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1337_10674_000031_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1337/10674/1337_10674_000031_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1337",
        "content": "But I was too late.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1337_10674_000031_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1337/10674/1337_10674_000031_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1337",
        "content": "The palace opened and the genius appeared, who, turning angrily to the princess, asked indignantly,",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1337_10674_000033_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1337/10674/1337_10674_000033_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1337",
        "content": "\"A pain in my heart,\" she replied hastily, \"obliged me to seek the aid of this little bottle.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1337_10674_000033_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1337/10674/1337_10674_000033_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1337",
        "content": "Feeling faint, I slipped and fell against the talisman, which broke.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1337_10674_000034_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1337/10674/1337_10674_000034_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1337",
        "content": "\"You are an impudent liar!\" cried the genius.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1337_10674_000035_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1337/10674/1337_10674_000035_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1337",
        "content": "\"I never saw them before,\" she answered, \"and you came in such a hurry that you may have picked them up on the road without knowing it.\" To this the genius only replied by insults and blows.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1337_10674_000036_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1337/10674/1337_10674_000036_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1337",
        "content": "While I was thus indulging my grief my host entered, and said, \"There is an old man downstairs who has brought your hatchet and slippers, which he picked up on the road, and now restores to you, as he found out from one of your comrades where you lived.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1337_10674_000037_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1337/10674/1337_10674_000037_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1337",
        "content": "\"I am a genius,\" he said, \"the son of the daughter of Eblis, prince of the genii.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1337_10674_000037_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1337/10674/1337_10674_000037_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1337",
        "content": "When he touched the ground, he rapped it with his foot; it opened, and we found ourselves in the enchanted palace, in the presence of the beautiful princess of the Ebony Isle. But how different she looked from what she was when I had last seen her, for she was lying stretched on the ground covered with blood, and weeping bitterly.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1337_10674_000039_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1337/10674/1337_10674_000039_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1337",
        "content": "She lifted up her eyes slowly, and looked sadly at me.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1337_10674_000042_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1337/10674/1337_10674_000042_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1337",
        "content": "\"Very well,\" said the genius, drawing his sword, \"take this, and cut off his head.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1337_10674_000045_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1337/10674/1337_10674_000045_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1337",
        "content": "\"How should I, when I never saw her before?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1337_10674_000046_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1337/10674/1337_10674_000046_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1337",
        "content": "\"Cut her head off,\" then, \"if she is a stranger to you, and I shall believe you are speaking the truth, and will set you at liberty.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1337_10674_000047_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1337/10674/1337_10674_000047_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1337",
        "content": "But the look of gratitude she gave me shook my courage, and I flung the sabre to the earth.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1337_10674_000050_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1337/10674/1337_10674_000050_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1337",
        "content": "The genius, however, paid no attention to my prayers, but said sternly, \"That is the way in which a genius treats the woman who has betrayed him.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1337_10674_000051_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1337/10674/1337_10674_000051_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1337",
        "content": "\"O genius!\" I cried, \"as you wish to spare my life, be generous, and spare it altogether.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1337_156963_000004_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1337/156963/1337_156963_000004_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1337",
        "content": "STUDY two",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1337_156963_000005_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1337/156963/1337_156963_000005_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1337",
        "content": "MAN'S RESPONSIBILITY FOR HIS ACTS.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1337_156963_000009_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1337/156963/1337_156963_000009_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1337",
        "content": "And when the woman saw that the tree was good for food and that it was a delight to the eye, and that the tree was to be desired to make one wise, she took of the fruit thereof, and did eat; and she gave also unto her husband with her and he did eat.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1337_156963_000016_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1337/156963/1337_156963_000016_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1337",
        "content": "Do they thereby commit a sin?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1337_156963_000016_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1337/156963/1337_156963_000016_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1337",
        "content": "Is the act necessarily wrong in itself?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1337_156963_000020_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1337/156963/1337_156963_000020_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1337",
        "content": "Most primitive peoples defined it as failure to perform certain ceremonial acts, or to bring tribute to the gods.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1337_156963_000020_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1337/156963/1337_156963_000020_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1337",
        "content": "The Hebrew people were the first to define right and wrong in terms of personal life and service.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1337_156963_000020_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1337/156963/1337_156963_000020_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1337",
        "content": "The temptation came from within rather than from without, and the responsibility of not choosing the best rested with the individual.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1337_156963_000021_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1337/156963/1337_156963_000021_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1337",
        "content": "One god, Ormuzd, was the embodiment of light and goodness. The other, Ahriman, represented darkness and evil.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1337_156963_000021_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1337/156963/1337_156963_000021_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1337",
        "content": "They traced all sin to the direct influence of Ahriman and the evil spirits that attended him.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1337_156963_000022_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1337/156963/1337_156963_000022_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1337",
        "content": "three.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1337_156963_000024_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1337/156963/1337_156963_000024_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1337",
        "content": "The serpent's words represent the natural inclinations that were struggling in the mind of the woman against her sense of duty. Note that in the story the temptation did not come to man through his appetite or his curiosity or his esthetic sense but through his wife whom God had given him.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1337_156963_000024_000009",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1337/156963/1337_156963_000024_000009.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1337",
        "content": "Are they thereby excused?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1337_156963_000024_000011",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1337/156963/1337_156963_000024_000011.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1337",
        "content": "How far did her experience reflect common human experience?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1337_156963_000024_000012",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1337/156963/1337_156963_000024_000012.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1337",
        "content": "What was the real nature of her act?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1337_156963_000025_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1337/156963/1337_156963_000025_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1337",
        "content": "The Hebrew word for sin (which means to miss the mark placed before each individual) vividly and aptly describes the real nature of sin.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    }
]